{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782184048001,"sessionID":"ses_10d8dd3bcffeaVGxb4zrU6ohlX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"539786454","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple key-value cache implementation.\n\n## createCache()\n\nReturns a new cache instance with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n\n```js\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value by its key. Returns `undefined` if the key does not exist.\n\n```js\nconst value = cache.get(key)\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value under a key. Returns the input value.\n\n```js\ncache.set(key, value)\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a value by its key. Returns `true` if the key existed, `false` otherwise.\n\n```js\nconst exists = cache.delete(key)\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n","filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/openrtk-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/openrtk-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","time":{"start":1782184047990,"end":1782184047999}},"id":"prt_ef2725fa4001WnVdP3ueNW8Nlo","sessionID":"ses_10d8dd3bcffeaVGxb4zrU6ohlX","messageID":"msg_ef2725bb6001a70FVzl56ucuuM"}}
